thread.title: Two Ohio police officers shot dead responding to 911 call

title: Two Ohio police officers shot dead responding to 911 call
text:
Two Ohio police officers shot dead responding to 911 call 8:33pm IST - 01:15 
Two Ohio police officers were shot to death on Saturday while responding to a domestic disturbance in the Columbus suburb of Westerville, and a suspect was wounded and is in custody, officials said. Nathan Frandino reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
